Sooooooooooooooooooooo...

The past few days were really fun just because of the awesome group of people I was with.


Yea, pretty much

Everyone is dancing to Queen  in my living room and IM missing it... so Im getting off the computer now I guess... I wish Katie was here... BUT IM SOOOOOOOOO glad Carrie and le Brito are here!! yes!!!!! Dance party flashbacks. GOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOD TIMES MAN!!!

AHHHHHHHHHHHHH... The past few days have been HELL!!!! And to make things worse I can NOT stop thinking about the past like I ALWAYS DO!!!! Everyone around me is having fun, moving on, enjoying the things they used to, doing things... what the hell am I doing or enjoying or anything?!?!?! When is the last time I hung out with an old friend or fucking left Petaluma?! I want to run back to about 2 years ago.... those were the days man... or I want to fucking move forward.... instead I am stuck and it sucks a whole fucking lot and I dunno what to do so Im just gunna get off the damn computer.

Well I came over to my moms this morning to get some stuff done.. but started thinking and got all distracted. I did call a few houses though and leave messages... which is kinda almost getting things done? heh.... So the past few days have just been stupid. We all went to Ambers a few night ago and it was fun for the most part.. the only dumb part was right after I came in all pissed off (I do not even remember WHY I was mad to begin with)... and saw Jesse and Vanessa setting up to go sleep where I had just been told no one could sleep (because I had fallen asleep there... and had to relocate) ANYWAY... I informed them that no one could sleep in that room and then they were like "ACTUALLY, no one can sleep in that BED... you don't know what your talking about.. yadda yadda." and me of course being in a bad moood to begin with instead of walking away I decided to go on and tell them they were wrong... yadda yadda.... and so it ended in me having to pee and Vanessa storming around the house drunk and pissed as hell at me.... Jesse was pissed at me too.... Oh well.. I did apologize for the way I went about the situation and Jesse seemed to be alright with me but Vanessa will not look at me. I think it is retarded seeing as how they were drunk and it was all just a stupid argument over a room... especially considering..... but I guess I should not be surprised.... and Carrie 'can't be around me' because she accused me of stealing money, which came out of no where and is completely retarded as well.... I have no idea what the fuck she is talking about... but instead of spreading rumors and shit she could talk to me.... whatever.... Im obviously too horrible or some shit.... raar.
This is pretty much the lowest point in my life so far. The hardest part is not diving in and going even lower. shit.

Yep.. pretty much. Arg.. you know I do not think anything would surprise me right now. I have stopped being surprised... Life is a huge pile of shit... and yet I feel no feeling about it except a calm... Fuck.

I have never felt this shitty. ever. i fucking hate life with a passion. not one good thing left... just a bunch of shit. and to top it off i have no one besides kent. i do not get it... how can people be so shitty and not even notice? even if they did notice.. they would not care... so yesterday i spent the day just sitting in a ball feeling absoutley lower than i have ever felt before knowing that they knew that and didnt care. never before have i done that or felt that horrible feeling that gets to the point where im not thinking anything at all.... just sitting empty... i have no clue what to do  but im pretty sure if my brain has to handle much more im going to fucking kill someone. i always just push anything bad to the back of my brain and dont think or sulk about it.... or just sit by myself ever... but i have no clue what else to do now that everything good is gone and the bad shit is fucking tearing my brain apart. I dont even know what this feeling is... mostly rage. i sit and fester this new rage that is most likely going to come out full force soon because its really fucking difficult to keep pushing aside. fuck you all.
hurm.. I dunno what to type, but I still felt like coming on LiveJournal. Life is pretty nuch the same as usual.... except for some things. Uh, I have no idea what to write. bye

So, I had an awesome adventure with Kent.. my freakin awesome boyfriend. (Yeah Bitch, Don't hate.)It was a great time filled with adventure and a long walk. Basically it fuckin ruled and I still have the greatest boyfriend ever. :::blush::: I was gunna write more, but it was indescribable. Kent (who is sitting right next to me. Im lucky aren't I) also blushed.... :::BLUSH:::   <~~~ Guy Blushes are bigger!

Yes.... I waited all day anxiously.. and had a fun night! I freakin love this feeling... which is why I must treat myself every so often.. yes sir eeeee.... It's late so I should not type long... next time I shall plan better and do it on a day I do not work afterward or get enough for work too.. hah 'cause damn Im gunna be tired.. oh well... worth it.. even though Kent turns into a boring ol' wall. I hate this part though.. the getting tired and all.. and not wanting to 'cause your just so content.. and then you feel like you are running out of play time..but eh... all good things must end.. i guess.... te he... I shall await another fun night.. hopefully with le Carrie as my random adventure partner on this one.. well.. felt like typing... but should go now and message Maika so Kent can get done and we can rest. ha. Later

So right as I sat to type Carrie got ready to leave... soooooooooooooooooooo I will update some other time I guess.... Eh my back is FUCKING KILLING MEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!! I am fuckin exausted as all hell.. eh.,.... ack... AND tomorrow I have to go to work like this... god damn it all!!  I need a cigarette like none other.... but oh.. look at that I have no fuckin money. great.  I have no idea what to write.. a crap load has happened..... Kents entire (seriously... like ALL of them) family hates me.. long story ... or stories rather. I have a lot of fun things coming up.. but I need some money... which I should be saving because next month we will have no where to live..... yep....  although I basically just go home to sleep now and get up and leave asap... 'cause the house is a fuckin hell hole and everyone is against everyone. I miss Mark and Nicole.. but I can not get a hold of them over any phone.... and I think they think Im mad at them... or something like that.. hurm, Im not sure.... On the bright side Kent got a job..... but we both still need better ones... urm. Happy side. We went to the river yesterday.. tons of fun.. too bad Kent and Danny had to work so they could not come. I took Rascal with us and he had tons of fun.... well I have a lot more junk to tell.. but do not feel like it. bye.

Sooooooooooooooooooooooooo a fuck load of shit has been happening lately... but Im not explaining all of it... in the long run CArrie hated us.. but then she hugged us and all was well.... and IM happy. Last night was super fun watching everyone get drunk 'cause it was like the first time I was not drinking with them while we were in a house. BUT.... next weekend shall be fun 'cause we are either drinking downtown and sleeping at Vanessa's or everyone is coming over to our house. AND we had our appointment at the Downtown River Apartments yesterday and I think we are going to get in... man I hope so!!!!!! One bedrooms are more uncommon than 2 bedrooms, so we will most likely get a 2 bedroom and it'll be awesome. The only bad thing about the apartments is that I can not have a dog over 25lbs and I want a medium dog. Well Im gunna go play speed with Kent.. soooo bye!

Mark taught me how to drive a stick shift yesterday and I am really good.. whoo hoo.. :o)  I love driving Kent's car and I get to drive it to work tomorrow.. te he

I went to the doctors yesterday and they took blood... ack. My tooth hurts though so I have to go back to the dentist because he did a shitty job. Dumb dentist.

Today was alright... considering. Don't ask.. Im just a dumb ass. However, in the end I learned a few people's true colors.. stuff I've known for awhile, but overlooked. oh wel.. shit happens. Misha..... Mark and Nicole's cat had her kittens today! There is 6 of them. I really want the little orange one... but everyone does so we will probably end up with a black one. We have our apartment appointment on Friday so I really really hope we get in... i have to get out of here! Hopefully Mark and Nicole will move with us and we can move into a house... and I get my puppy!!! well..... bed time.

HAPPY EASTER!!!

Im just chillen at my mom's house. Kent is at home sleeping 'cause he worked graveyard last night. I doubt that he'd come down here anyway.... he hasn't wanted to do ANYTHING lately..... like leaving the house is some HUGE event... and leave Santa Rosa is a long journey.I  don't get it... he used to like to do things. Now he just wants to stay home all the time, play the computer, smoke, and sleep.... that's it. Oh well..... hopefully it's a phase.. plus we are moving to P-town soon and then our house will be way more convenient. yup My damn lap top will not turn on, so I can not use the internet at my house.... I am going to the computer place next week hopefully to ask about it. Brito and Nessa stayed at my house last night... 'twas fun fun... the Sims 2 is fuckin awesome... so we got extremely stoned and played the computer. We put on the Simpsons after that, but all 3 of us passed out right when we layed down at like 2:30.... then we had to get up early 'cause I had to drive them home and stuff for Easter crap.Ack.. Im falling alseep... i think Ill go shower.. bye

Sooooo I have been saying Im going to do this huge update.. yadda yadda... and now I have finally gotten ready to type.. but first I need some spaghetti... so I'M going to go make some first.....


:::making spaghetti:::

WTF?!?! It's almost 12?!!?!?!?   Maybe I won't update.. hurm....

Okay.. water is boiling... Mark and Nicole want some too so I have to make a bunch.... rarg

So... Kent's stepmom Paula died like a week ago so the house has been kind of a mess... Kent's poor dad is not taking it very well at all.... I feel sooo bad for the poor guy. It was not expected that she'd go so soon. She just started convulsing and throwing up blood... all but one of her vital organs shut down and her heart was the only thing working... but only with help from machines.... sooo needless to say she died. I have never had someone I live with die... and it was sad... the whole house was just a sad place to be. 

Carrie and I did acid together the next day and that was fun. Kent wanted to go home... so once again Carrie and I dropped together and didn't get to hang out...... Oh well... there was a lot of people here so I just stayed up all night and walked around outside... fun fun fun on acid....

Then the 1st was Kent's mom's b-day so Kent' Vanessa, Joey and I went up to Williits... it was really fun.... Kent's grandma was wasted when we got there... but the food was awesome. On the way we saw ice age 2... hahah.. really funny.... and did a crapload of nitrous in the car....  I spent like all weekend with Ness and it was fun fun.

Yesterday Kent's dad bought Kent and I a brand new awesome computer and an all-in-one printer deal.. it prints scans copies and all that.... he bought computers for most of us with his inheritance and helped everyone out.... his dad is freakin' awesome.

Kent might buy a car from Vanessa's dad.. it's pretty sweet..... uh huh that'll be kool... its a stick so we could both learn how to drive stick.

Fuckin' Shyler stil has my money..... rararararara... and we fuckin got jacked in P-town for hella money because we are retarded..... but yeah... oh well.....

Im gunna go get high and check on my food...... later

So.. I will do the whole official update later.. but I felt like typing a little now.... Sooooooooo Vanessa, Kent, Joey, and I are in Willits rihgt now for Kent's mom's bday.... uh huh... the drive was alright, but when we got here Kent's Grandma was wasted.. te he.... we ate a bomb ass dinner and stayed up hella late doing nothing.. but it was fun anyways.... and now I have to go butter my food.. yum yum crepes..... yuuuuuuuuuuuuuummm!!
Sooo.. a shitload happened this weekend but i do not feel like fully updating... so ill do it later.

Is it just me or does this seem like a transitional period?... not just for me... but everybody seems to be in a transition right now. No one is really where they want or need to be.... but struggling on their way there instead. Some of us have gotten lost..... but so far no one has completely given up..... yeah... these are weird days... I miss the old days soo much, but at the same time I am pretty excited to see what will come... I should try and be like Carrie and just live for the moment.

Alright.. moving on. I put some lasagna in the microwave,,,, it said to put it on for 5 minutes... rotate and then put on for another 2.... but I figured since the microwave has one of those trays that continually spins.. the rotation was unnecessary... sooooo I just put it on for 7 minutes and left..... I wonder if it is done yet..... I shall go check... yep it's done.. but i stepped in fucking dog pee on the way to the garage (fucking DOG!!!) MmMmMmMm.. veggie lasagna.. Kent bought a bunch of veggie stuff for me when he went shopping with his dad... whoo hooo....    :-P  

So.. none of this is really relevant, but I do not have to work until 3:45 today and Kent wanted me to wait for him to get off work instead of going to P-town.. so Im pretty bored. I did get high after dropping Kent off and fell asleep again for 2 hours... man oh man I had one CrAzY ass dream! I can not even fully explain it... it was awesome though! I love dreaming and I always have the most interesting dreams after getting stoned.... go figure eh? haha At  Vanessa's the other day Kent and I decided we want 2 Nintendo DSs.... I dunno if I should put an s or es..... hum.... well anyways then we will not be so bored in the Phoenix all the time... haha.. Hide N go Seek was pretty fucking fun though.


I finally got my car from my mom... yippee... freedom to go to Petaluma and not have to freeze at the bus stop..... plus now I can drive everyone home and stuff. Damn... I just finished eating .. that was hella bomb! Well... now I need to go smoke.. so I guess Im done on LJ.... gah.. I don't wanna work today!! I hate closing! raar No work tomorrow... whooo hoo

So, this whole anxiety thing kinda makes me want to punch myself in the face!!!! I am so sick of dealing with this constant anxiety that NEVER leaves anymore.. before I only had anxiety some of the time.. but now it is worse than ever..... always there lurking and then spurting out in sudden panic attacks. This is dumb... and I do not know how to control this unnecessary feeling... ack!.... I feel sick. It sucks even more because now when I do hard drugs it only makes it worse... acid was fun for a few hours until the anxiety kicked in and yesterday I was on e.... ecstasy.. IM supposed to be happy right? I usually am.. but this time I freaked out.... left P-town with out saying bye to anyone.... sat in the car.... felt happy for like an hour or so and then I was just anxious for the rest of it.... aaaaaaaah I hate my brain... stupid stupid stupid brain!!!! I hate this and I can't control it at all... its taking over and I kinda wanna just crawl in a box and never come out again.

I wanted to go downtown today 'cause no one was there yesterday... but I have to work tomorrow morning... ack. Oh well, I figure it is all worth it because my car will be all the way paid off soon (whoo hoo, one less thing to worry about, we can start saving for Kent's car, and we will be moving to Petaluma soon hopefully... then I'll have a lot more time downtown and my own place! Plus, I get to move with the most amazing person ever, continue our life and get a little puppy... hehe... Life is finally moving forward and I feel like it will all work out in the end... so I guess I have to make sacrifices before my life works out. Im so lucky to have a guy like Kent :::smile:::

Im just sitting in my room OXed out listening to music and scratching scratchers... waiting for Kent to get off work. We are doing e and heading downtown....yippee!! I hope you peoples are down there tonight, I want to see you! Yep Yep... As you can tell Im pretty bored. I rollerbladed to Walgrrens..... I have not rollerbladed in So long! It was kinda fun and way faster than walking.... Well, guess I'll get back to these scrathers... hope I win some monies!!!! Laterz!
A lot of shit has happened... obviously since I have not been on here is HHHHHHEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEELLLLLLLLLLLLLLLAAAAAAAAAAAA days!!! BUT not I have internet on my laptop!!!! yes yes yes yes yes!!!

GODDAMN IT!!!!!! Why is it when 1 thing goes wrong everything else has to go wrong too? ...... People are dumb.... including myself.... yeah- long story...IM so goddamn frustrated with my life.. whatever...I feel like Im going to throw up again.... bye.
Im just sitting here with my favorite ppl ever drinking and watching movies... yes..... fun shit. vbye

Hurm.. I dunno if Carrie still read livejournals... but ..... if you do... than you should call me.... I heard you aren't mad anymore but thought I wouldn't talk to you... but I thought it was the other way around.. yeah.. class bye.

I just got home and I haven't been here in forever it seems like... hurm. Brito was supposed to come over.. but my damn bus was late... so I got home late and she doesn't have a damn cell phone.... gah... so she left and is probably pretty pissed.... damn public transportation... so now Im eating a sandwich and listening to Afroman... good times good times... I have to clean the whole damn house... meeeeeeeh.. I do not want to! I have nothing to say but I felt like updating so..... yeah
Best snack ever- pita bread with onion and red bell peppers....... yum yum yum. :::licks lips:::

I do not remember anything after walking back onto the portch and finishing my drink...but I still can NOT believe I would do that to someone who I care so much about (don't ask.... you had to be there)... yeah so I wake up and I was like wtf?!?!when did I fall asleep and what the hell happened last night.... I was still drunk so I smoked a cigarette and went back to sleep......Everyone wakes up..... Vanessa tells me everything that went on the night before..... Lessons for everyone to learn

#1 Do NOT give a drunk person weird orange putty, if they find it themselves- confiscate it.. and hide it.

#2 Do not let drunk people share the weird orange putty with other drunk people.

#3 The weird orange putty melts easily with body heat.

#4 It is just about impossible to get the weird orange putty out of hair, clothes, beds, carpets, and fingernails.

#5 Water does not help... it just gets sticky. 



What the hell is the purpose of this weird orange putty?!?!

I just spent SOOOOOOOOOOO long doing this online shit for history.... blah blah.. Im only half done but, hey since I actually started I feel accomplished.. haha.... doesn't take much to make a slacker feel good eh? Now let's go get wasted!

Last night was so fun... Kent's godmother's B-day whoo hoooo.

So Tony and Kent finally meet me downtown at like 9... once they got there we did e and walked around.... wow Kent and Tony were rollin downtown... that was amusing... then finally mine hit in the car... yes..... arrive at the hotel.... drink a fuckload of Whiskey... smoke a chewy blunt.... smoke like 8947239847298.39472 normal blunts..... smoke the roaches to them all...... stay up all fucking night.... haha.. we were up drinking 'till past 7 in the morning....and sitting on the steps smoking cigarettes at like 10... Kent was amazingly fucked up.... he passed out for a bit and then Sabrina came out and said we could go take the bed in the other room... so I finally get Kent up and in there..... We both lay there WIDE awake staring at everything and all of a sudden Kent sits up and goes "How the hell did we end up in a bed by ourselves? Weren't we just in the living room.... wtf?!?!Uhh.. I don't remember coming in here at all" Wow...... no more alchohol for Kent..... yeah.. a lot of other things happened... too lazy to type and I have to go do shit before I go out tonight.. whoop whoop..... by kids.
Hum... I do not remember half of last night.... but I Do remember standing in my room and deciding I wanted to leave again... so I got dressed and snuck out the back.. haha it was random...... huh.
Fuck you Kylie, I love you, but FUCK YOU!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
My life has changed so much in the past 2 months... it's crazy.
vanessa is making little pizzas!!! score! I love you all!

I forgot to announce that VANESSA SMOKED WEED!!!!!! I passed it to her in rotation and she hit it!!!!!! I was SHOCKED.. granted she was drunk, but usually while drunk she's all "Eww... you're smoking weed!" (even though she will smoke 482734982.328 cigarettes) haha I was all "OMG?! Did you just hit that?!?!" And she looked at me and was like "yep" and then smoked the rest of the rotation... wowza!!! I knew it would happen! My lil' Nessa... hahaha

She kept insisting that someone tried to strangle me because my neck looks like a war zone (sgfhkjhjfdkdsjalkd!!!) so I just told her the truth. It shut her up... but now she will not stop asking questions and insisting on meeting him... damn it.

I had sooo much fun last night!hahaha... I was on stage the whole time dancing like crazy... I saw Nina and like attacked her with a hug.. she was like "I thought that was you on stage, but wasn't sure." She absolutely refused to dance... pffft. Maria chilled with us last night too.... fuuuuuun stuff- I love remembering all the old museum days and how much we hate all the people there.... it's like a cult, I swear. Saw Tony at a bar...he was hilarious..... Kent and I started walking to his aunt's (long ass fuckin walk)...but when I stopped to pee Adie drove by and picked us up... score!!! Yeah... good times, had to get up today to get the oil in my car changed (blah)...but oh well.....:::dances:::
